entries.s_36: Hey soldier, I need a volunteer for an important job. You want to make some credits?
entries.s_40: I need you to pull some guard duty outside the walls to keep the enemy from waltzing in our front door.
entries.s_42: I think I can do that.
entries.s_46: Look, take my advice and go get some training. You look too green for anything we have here.
entries.s_50: When I give you orders soldier, you carry them out.  No negotiations. Now get to your post before I put a boot to your backside.
entries.s_51: All you have to do is go to a guard post and attract their attention. Sound good?
entries.s_55: You're back. Can I get you to do some more of that guard duty soldier?
entries.s_61: I sent your orders to your data pad. Good luck!
entries.s_64: You got skills soldier. If I get out of here I'll send a message to High Command with my report. Until then, take these credits.
entries.s_69: You better go get the anti-virus. I don't have time to mess with someone turning on me later!
entries.s_77: Here is your post. Good luck.
entries.s_90: Here I am. Knee deep in undead...thank the Emperor I have my blaster.
